parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The transmission disengagement and unintended shifting can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or roll backwards, leading to accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: Transmission completely disengages while driving
vehicle comes to a complete stop
vehicle rolls backwards while in park
vehicle shifts into park without warning
vehicle jerks violently and stalls without warning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the fuel system can cause the vehicle to lose motive power, leading to accidents or stranding the driver.
symptoms: Vehicle loses motive power
check engine warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the backup camera can reduce visibility and increase the risk of accidents, especially when reversing, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The backup camera flickers
shows a mirror flip image
or fails to display an image
making it unreliable for safety.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Unintended Acceleration due to Pedal Adjustment
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration can cause loss of vehicle control, leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine RPM increases suddenly
and the vehicle speed jumps
when adjusting the pedals using the switch mounted on the driver's seat. The vehicle may accelerate rapidly
even when the driver is not pressing the accelerator pedal.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The intermittent failure of the rearview camera can cause the driver to lose visibility while reversing, increasing the risk of accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The rearview camera cuts on and off
the image is inverted
the picture is clear but everything is on the wrong side
the camera malfunctions while reversing.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the automatic door lock system can cause the doors to reopen unexpectedly, potentially allowing unauthorized access to the vehicle or its contents.
symptoms: The doors reopen by themselves after being locked
this occurs while the vehicle is parked.
